Class Link

java.lang.Object
Link
public class Link
extends java.lang.Object
A Model class for the links in the solo adventure. A Link contains a story id for the scene it is showed in, a target id for the scene it will direct the player to and a description that tells the player what choosing this Link/option will do. The Link also contains an id of its own that is handled by a database.

    • Link

      public Link​(int id, int storyId, int targetId, java.lang.String description)
      Constructs a link with an id and data on where it leads, which scene it is linked to and what it does story-wise.
      Parameters:
      id - The id of the link.
      storyId - The id of the scene to which the link is linked.
      targetId - The id of the scene to which the link leads.
      description - A description of what the player does if it chooses this link.
